Ingaruka z'ubwandu bwa coronavirus (COVID-19) zigaragaza ko ibintu bimeze nk'ibyo mu bihugu by'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Igihugu cy'ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza byemeza ko, nubwo biri ku rugero rutandukanye bitewe n'igihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kirimo cyandura vuba mu bihugu byose.
Dukurikije ibyagezweho n'u Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bikwiye kongera ubushobozi bwabo bwo kwihanganira umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazacyeneye kwitabwaho mu buryo bw'ubuzima, cyane cyane ubuvuzi bukomeye.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, hari imibare myinshi y'abantu banduye indwara ya PN na SIDA, mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko ikoranabuhanga ry'indwara ya coronavirus ari ryo ryatumye iyi ndwara ibaho, ubu ikaba yitwa coronavirus acute respiratory syndrome 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara zituruka ku cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 ziswe indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu byaragaragaye ko abagera kuri 80% by'abantu bafite COVID-19 bafite indwara nke, cth. indwara z'imyenda yo mu mwuka zifite cyangwa zitagira pneumonia, kandi abenshi muri abo barwayi barakira.
Mu bice 14%, COVID-19 igenda ihinduka indwara ikomeye cyane igasaba ubuvuzi mu bitaro, mu gihe mu bindi 6% by'abanduye, indwara ikomeye igasaba ubuvuzi bukomeye.
Imfu z'abarwayi bavurirwa mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni hafi 4%.
Muri iki cyifuzo, twagerageje kureba uko COVID-19 ikomeza kubaho mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) n'ubwongereza, ndetse turagereranya ibyo bihugu n'Akarere ka Hubei mu Bushinwa.
