Hari ibitekerezo byinshi ku birebana n'aho icyorezo cya mbere cyiswe "umurwayi w'umubare w'ubusa" cyavuye.
Umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye ko afite coronavirus nshya ashobora kugaruka ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan, Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi, umubare w'abanduye Coronavirus muri Hubei wiyongereye buhoro buhoro.
Ibi byago byiganjemo ibijyanye n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Huanan, rigurisha n'ibinyabuzima, kandi hari igitekerezo cy'uko virusi ikomoka kuri imwe muri izi nyamaswa; cyangwa, mu yandi magambo, ko ifite inkomoko zoonotic.
Ku itariki ya 30 Ukuboza, umugwi w'abaganga bo mu bitaro bya Wuhan Central Hospital wahamagariye bagenzi babo "kurwara coronavirus nka SARS".
Abaganga umunani barimo Li Wenliang, bari barahawe igihano na polisi kubera gukwirakwiza ibinyoma, undi witwa Ai Fen, yari yarashimuswe n'abayobozi be kubera ko yabyukije.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan Municipal Health Commission yahise itanga itangazo ku wa 31 Ukuboza, maze itangaza ko WHO ifite ikibazo cy'indwara.
Ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bw'ibihaha bitamenyekanye bihagije byatangajwe ku nzego z'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan kugira ngo hatangire iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu bindi bice by'u Bushinwa, ifashijwe n'impunzi z'umwaka mushya w'u Bushinwa n'i Wuhan zikaba ari hub y'ingendo ndetse n'aho hubatswe gari ya moshi zikomeye.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwavuze ko hashize umunsi umwe habonetse abantu bashya bagera ku 140, barimo babiri i Beijing n'undi umwe i Shenzhen.
Amakuru yemewe nyuma yaho agaragaza ko abantu 6,174 bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso ku wa 20 Mutarama 2020.Ku wa 26 Werurwe, Amerika yarushijeho Ubushinwa na Italiya ku mubare munini w'abanduye ku isi.Ku wa 9 Mata 2020, abantu barenga miliyoni 1.61 bamaze kuvugwa ku isi; abantu barenga 97,000 bamaze gupfa n'abantu barenga 364,000 bamaze gukira.
