Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cya mbere cyemejwe cyatowe ku wa 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan; raporo imwe itarakemezwa igaragaza ko icyorezo cya mbere cyabaye ku wa 17 Ugushyingo.
Dr Zhang Jixiang yabonye icyorezo cy'indwara z'ubwonko zitamenyekanye ku wa 26 Ukuboza, nyuma yaho ibitaro bye bimenyesha CDC ya Wuhan Jianghan ku wa 27 Ukuboza.
Igerageza ry'ubwoko bw'ibinyabuzima bwa mbere ku bipimo by'abarwayi ku wa 27 Ukuboza 2019 ryagaragaje ko hari coronavirus nka SARS.
Itangazo ry'abaturage ryasohowe na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan Municipal ku wa 31 Ukuboza.
WHO yatangaje ko ari umunsi umwe.
Mu gihe cy'iki cyemezo, abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan bari barahawe umuburo n'igipolisi kubera "gutangaza ibinyoma" ku byerekeye iki cyorezo.
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa mu ntangiriro yavuze ko nta "bihamya bifatika" byerekana ko abantu banduye indwara z'indwara.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bw'inkomoko nyuma y'aho, byiswe n'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti ry'u Bushinwa Xi Jinping ko ari "intambara y'abaturage" yo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Mu gihe cy'ikibazo cyiswe "kwihererana gukomeye cyane mu mateka y'abantu", ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama hatangajwe ko hakomeje gufungwa abantu bagera kuri 57 miliyoni, bigatuma abantu batinjira no kuva mu mujyi wa Wuhan, kandi ko byamaze gukwirakwizwa mu migi 15 ya Hubei.
Imodoka z'abikorera zabuzanyijwe mu mijyi.
Mu bihugu byinshi, kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa (itariki ya 25 Mutarama) byarahagaritswe.
Abayobozi batangaje ko hubakwa ibitaro by'agateganyo, ibitaro bya Huoshenshan, bizarangira mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hari undi bitaro byubatswe, ni ukuvuga ibitaro bya Leishenshan, kugira ngo bikomeze kwita ku barwayi b'inyongera.
Uretse ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 bya Wuhan nk'ikigo cy'amateraniro n'inkino, bihinduka ibitaro by'agateganyo. Ku wa 26 Mutarama, guverinoma yatangiye ingamba zikurikira zo guhashya icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga itangazo ry'ubuzima ku ba mukerarugendo no kwagura ikiruhuko cya Festival y'Icyumweru.
Kaminuza n'amashuri hirya no hino mu gihugu na byo byafunzwe.
Hong Kong na Macau byatangiye ingamba zitandukanye, cyane cyane ku bijyanye n'amashuri na kaminuza.
Ingamba zo gukora imirimo ya kure zatangiye mu turere tumwe two mu Bushinwa.
Hari gahunda yo guhagarika ingendo mu karere ka Hubei no hanze yarwo.
Imodoka zitwara abantu zagiye zisubizwa, ndetse n'inzu ndangamurage zo mu Bushinwa zose zafunzwe by'agateganyo.
Mu mijyi myinshi, abantu bagenzurwa n'abaturage, kandi bivugwa ko abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (baba kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bahanganye n'ingamba zo kubuza abantu kujya mu mahanga.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho iminsi 14 yo gushyira mu kato abanyamahanga bose binjira mu mujyi. Ku wa 23 Werurwe, Ubushinwa bw'ibanze bwatanze icyorezo kimwe gusa mu minsi itanu, muri iki gihe uwo munyeshuri yari agarutse i Guangzhou avuye i Istanbul.
Ku itariki ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Bushinwa Li Keqiang yatangaje ko ubwandu bw'icyorezo mu gihugu cyabo bwabaye ingume kandi ko ubwandu bwacyo bwagenzurwa n'u Bushinwa.
Ku munsi umwe, ibihano by'urugendo byaragabanyijwe mu ntara ya Hubei, uretse mu mujyi wa Wuhan, nyuma y'amezi abiri igihugu cy'u Bushinwa cyashyizeho itegeko rivuga ko kwinjira ku gihugu cyabo binyuze mu visa cyangwa ku ruhushya rw'abaturage bizagororerwa kuva ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe, nta makuru asobanutse neza ku gihe iyo gahunda izarangira.
Abashaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsulat.
Leta y'u Bushinwa yashishikarije ubucuruzi n'inganda kongera gufungura ku itariki ya 30 Werurwe, ndetse itanga inguzanyo z'amafaranga ku bigo. Inama y'Igihugu yatangaje ko umunsi wo kwicuza uzatangira n'iminota itatu y'ikiruhuko saa kumi n'ebyiri za saa kumi za mu gitondo ku itariki ya 4 Mata, mu gihe Leta y'u Bushinwa yasabye imiryango kugaragariza icyubahiro kuri interineti kuko ikurikiza imfungwa zo mu mubiri kugira ngo icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyihinduke.
COVID-19 yemejwe ko yanduye Koreya y'Epfo ku wa 20 Mutarama 2020 iturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare habayeho kwiyongera kw'ibimenyetso by'ibimenyetso by'abanduye, ahanini bikaba byatewe n'amateraniro yo mu mujyi wa Daegu y'ishyaka rishya ry'idini ryitwa Yesu Shincheonji Church.
Abayoboke ba Shincheonji basuye Daegu bavuye i Wuhan bakekwaho kuba aribo bateje iki cyorezo.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bantu 9,336 bari muri iryo dini, abantu 1,261 cyangwa 13% bavuze ko bafite ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko imiburo yo mu rwego rwo hejuru ku itariki ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, abantu barenga 2,000 bamaze kwandura muri Koreya, biyongeraho 3,150 ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare.
Inzu zose za gisirikare za Koreya y'Epfo zahagaritswe nyuma y'uko ibizamini byemeza ko abasirikare batatu banduye iyi virusi.
Ibihe by'indege na byo byarahuye n'ingaruka kandi ibyo byarahindutse. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda ifatwa nk'igikorwa cyakwirakwiriye kandi gikorana neza kurusha ibindi ku isi cyo gukaraba abaturage kugira ngo babone virusi, no kwiherera abantu bose banduye no gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abantu bahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo gukaraba bwarimo gutanga raporo ku bw'ibimenyetso by'abimukira bashya ku isi yose binyuze mu porogaramu za telefoni zigendanwa, gupima virusi y'umushongi wa kera ibipimo byatanzwe ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima bigatuma abantu bagera ku 20,000 bageragezwa buri munsi.
Igihugu cya Koreya y'Epfo cyatangaje ko gahunda yacyo yo kurwanya iki cyorezo cy'indwara ya Corona imaze kugera ku rwego rwo hejuru nubwo kitari cyarayogoje umujyi wose.
Abenshi mu bakoreya basinye ku nyandiko y'ubujurire cyangwa basaba ko Moon yirukanwa kubera ibyo bavuga ko ari amakosa ya leta ku cyorezo, cyangwa se bashimira uko yabyitabiriye.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, byavuzwe ko Koreya y'Epfo ifite umubare muto w'abanduye ku munsi mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bine.
Ku itariki ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku itariki ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bashya bazaza mu mahanga bazaba bari mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nkuko byatangajwe n'itangazamakuru ku itariki ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo imaze kwakira ibisabwa byo gufashwa mu gupima virusi mu bihugu 121 bitandukanye.
Irani yatangaje ko ku itariki ya 19 Gashyantare i Qom, abantu babiri bishwe n'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2, nkuko Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi yabitangaje.
Mu ngamba za mbere leta yashyizeho zo kwirinda ibizahitana abantu harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, imikino, n'amasengesho yo ku wa gatanu, no gufunga kaminuza, ibigo by'uburezi bwa kaminuza n'amashuri.
Iran yatanze miliyari eshanu z'amafaranga yo kurwanya iyi virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato imijyi yahuye n'icyorezo, kandi ko abantu bonyine ari bo bazajya mu kato.
Inshingano zo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi zatangajwe mu kwezi kwa gatatu, nubwo imihanda myinshi ikomeje guhagarara mbere ya Nowruz y'umwaka mushya w'Abaperesi.
Ifunguro ry'aba Shia i Qom rizakomeza gufungurirwa abajya gusura abantu kugeza ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020.
Nubwo hari ikirego cy'uko icyorezo cyageze ku rwego rwo muri Irani, ibihugu birenga icumi byari byakurikiranye ko byasubiye muri Irani ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko icyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha 388 byatangajwe na guverinoma ya Irani kugeza icyo gihe.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, aho 23 mu 290 bayigize bagaragaye ko bageze kuri virusi ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye inzego z'uburoko za Irani kurekura burundu abarwanashyaka bazira uburenganzira bw'ikiremwamuntu bafunzwe bazira imyigaragambyo idafite umutekano, ndetse no kurekura imfungwa zose zifite uburenganzira bw'ikirenga.
Yavuze ko hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwira muri ibi bigo byafunze nka za gereza, aho usanga nta buvuzi buhagije buhari.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, guverinoma ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye ku munsi, ari umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye muri icyo gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Abantu 12 cyangwa benshi mu bayobozi ba leta cyangwa abahoze ari abayobozi b'ibihugu by'amahanga, barapfuye bazize iyo ndwara kugeza ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yaboneragaho abantu bashya 50 bagerwaho na coronavirus buri saha n'undi muntu umwe wapfa buri minota icumi.
Abategetsi ba OMS bavuga ko mu gihugu cya Iran hari abantu bashobora kuba banduye inshuro eshanu ugereranyije n'abavugwa.
Nanone kandi, byumvikanisha ko ibihano Amerika yafatiye Irani bishobora gutuma igihugu kitabasha guhangana n'icyorezo cy'iyi virusi.
Komisiyo nkuru y'umuryango w'abibumbye ishinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu byoroha ku bihugu byugarijwe n'icyorezo, harimo na Iran.
Icyorezo cyemejwe ko cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ku wa 31 Mutarama, ubwo abantu babiri b'abashyitsi bo mu Bushinwa bageragezwaga ko banduye SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Ibikorwa by'ubugenzacyaha byatangiye kwiyongera cyane, bituma leta y'u Butaliyani isaba ko ingendo zose ziva mu Bushinwa zijya mu Bushinwa zihagarikwa ndetse n'itangazo ry'imimerere y'ubutagondwa.
Nyuma hakurikiyeho hakemurwa icyorezo cya COVID-19, hatangirana n'ibimenyetso 16 byemejwe mu ntara ya Lombardy ku wa 21 Gashyantare.Ku wa 22 Gashyantare, Itorero ry'Abaminisitiri ryatangaje itegeko rishya ryo guhagarika icyorezo, harimo no gushyira mu kato abantu barenga 50,000 baturutse mu turere 11 dutandukanye two mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yagize ati "Mu karere k'icyorezo, kwinjira no gusohoka ntibizemewe.
Ku itariki ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'u Butaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na za kaminuza bifungwa burundu mu gihugu hose ubwo Ubutaliyani bwari bugeze ku gipimo cy'urupfu rwa 100.
Imikino yose ikomeye, harimo imikino ya shampiyona ya Serie A, yagombaga kuba yafunze kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yahagaritswe burundu ku gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse guhagarika ibikorwa hafi ya byose by'ubucuruzi uretse ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'ubuvuzi. Ku itariki ya 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani Gishinzwe Ubuvuzi, Ubuvuzi, Gusubiramo no Gutabara Indwara (SIAARTI) cyasohoye inama ku bijyanye n'amahame y'ubuvuzi ku bijyanye n'imikorere y'ibipimo by'ubuvuzi bishobora gukoreshwa.
Ku wa 19 Werurwe, u Butaliyani bwarushije u Bushinwa kuba igihugu gifite umubare munini w'abantu bapfa bazize coronavirus ku isi nyuma yo gutanga raporo y'abantu 3,405 bapfuye bazize iki cyorezo.
