Raporo ya CNN ivuga ko kubona abaturage benshi bo mu Butaliyani bafite ubwandu bw'amafaranga menshi n'ubushobozi buke bwo gupima abantu bose banduye iyi virusi kugeza ubu bishobora kuba ari byo byatumye umubare w'abapfa wiyongera.
Igisubizo cy'Ubwongereza kuri iyi virusi cyabanje kugaragara ko ari kimwe mu bihugu byugarijwe cyane n'iki cyorezo, kandi kugeza ku wa 18 Werurwe 2020, guverinoma y'Ubwongereza ntiyagenzerezaga abaturage bayo uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo gufungwa mu buryo bw'imibereho myiza cyangwa gushyira mu kato abantu benshi.
