Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, guverinoma yatangaje ko ahantu hose ho kuruhukira nko mu mabyiniro no mu mikino hagomba gufungwa vuba uko bishoboka kose, kandi isezeranya ko izishyura abakozi bagera kuri 80% by'imishahara y'abakozi kugeza ku gipimo cya £2,500 buri kwezi kugira ngo birinde ubushomeri muri icyo kibazo. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo gufunga abantu, abuza abantu guterana inshuro zirenze ebyiri no kugabanya ingendo n'ibikorwa byo hanze ku byo byemejwe ko ari ngombwa rwose.
