Ibihugu bigenzura abantu gusa bajyanywe mu bitaro bizahabwa amanota meza cyane ku kigero cya % cy'ibizamini ugereranyije n'ibihugu bigenzura abantu bose, baba bafite ibimenyetso cyangwa badafite, abandi bose ni kimwe.
Gukaraba intoki (cyangwa gukaraba intoki), nanone bizwi ku izina ry'isuku, ni igikorwa cyo gukaraba intoki zigamije gukuraho ubutaka, ibinure, uturemangingo cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakwiriye.
Gukaraba intoki buri gihe n'isabune mu "minsi y'akaga" runaka y'umunsi bifasha kwirinda indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'ibicurane n'indwara z'amaraso, zikagera mu kanwa.
Umuntu ashobora no kwandura indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, urugero nk'icyorezo cy'ibicurane cyangwa se se igituntu, urugero, iyo atarakarabye intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, mu mazuru cyangwa mu kanwa (cth., mucous membrane).
Ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi byo mu munsi aho umuntu ahanagura intoki akoresheje isabune ni ibi: mbere na nyuma yo gukaraba amazi menshi, nyuma yo gusukura imbeho y'umwana cyangwa guhindurira imyenda, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya no mbere na nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gukemura inyama zitagizwe, amafi cyangwa inyoni.
Iyo nta mazi n'isabune bihari, umuntu ashobora gukaraba intoki akoresheje umukungugu.
Mbere, mu gihe, no nyuma yo gutegura ibyokurya.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku barwayi.
Nyuma yo guhindura imyenda cyangwa gusukura abana bari bamaze gukoresha ubwiherero.
Nyuma yo gukubita mu mazuru, gukorora cyangwa kwishima.
Nyuma yo gukora ku nyamaswa, ku biribwa by'inyamaswa cyangwa ku mafi y'inyamaswa.
Isuku y'amaboko mu buvuzi yerekeza ku bikorwa by'isuku bifitanye isano n'uburyo bwo kwivuza.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukoresha umuti cyangwa gukoresha imiti bishobora gutuma indwara zitabasha gukwirakwira cyangwa kugabanya.
Intego y'ingenzi y'ubuvuzi bwo gukaraba intoki ni ugukura intoki ku ndwara (bakiteri, virusi cyangwa izindi mikorobe zishobora gutera indwara) n'ibikomoka ku bidukikije bishobora guteza akaga cyangwa indwara.
Ibi ni ingenzi cyane cyane ku bantu bakora ibiribwa cyangwa bakora mu buvuzi, ariko kandi ni ingenzi cyane ku baturage muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite inyungu nyinshi ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cya grippe, coronavirus n'izindi ndwara zandura; kwirinda ibitera kwandura imyanya ndangagitsina; kugabanya ubwandu bw'ubuhumekero;
kandi bagagabanya umubare w'abana bapfa igihe bavukaga.
Ubushakashatsi bwo mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko gukora neza imikorere yo gukaraba intoki bizatuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu bakura neza.
Mu bihugu byateye imbere, umubare w'abapfa mu bana bahitanwa n'indwara zo mu mutwe n'indwara zo mu bwoko bwa cirrhosis ushobora kugabanuka bashyiraho imihindagurikire y'imyitwarire, urugero nko gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune.
Iyo ngamba yoroheje ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abantu bapfa bazize iyo ndwara, ikagabanukaho hafi 50%.
Gufata imiti ikora mu gihe umuntu yiyuhagira intoki bishobora kugabanya ibice bitatu by'ibicurane by'amaraso, kandi ibyo bigereranywa no gutanga amazi meza mu turere dukennye.
48% by'abantu bafite ikibazo cy'indwara y'amaraso, bashobora kwifashisha isabune mu gukaraba intoki. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni bwo buryo bwonyine bw'ingirakamaro kandi bworoheje bwo kwirinda indwara z'amaraso n'indwara z'ubuhumekero (ARI), nk'uko bikorwa mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage ku isi hose.
Impanuka y'amaraso, ari yo ARI y'ingenzi, ni yo ihitana abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, igahitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Imyembere n'impuha z'ibihaha byombi bituma abana bagera hafi kuri miriyoni 3.5 bapfa buri mwaka.
UNICEF ivuga ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo gukaraba bishobora gukiza abantu benshi kurusha urukingo rumwe cyangwa imiti yose, bikagabanya hafi kimwe cya kabiri cy'abapfa bazize indwara z'amaraso, bikagabanya kimwe cya kane cy'abapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Gukaraba intoki akenshi bijyana no gukora ibindi bikorwa by'isuku nk'uko biri muri gahunda y'amazi, isuku n'isuku (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki bishobora no kurinda impetigo ziterwa no guhura n'umuntu imbonankubone.
Ingaruka mbi nke zo gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane ni uko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutuma uruhu rwononekara bitewe n'uko uruhu rwabaye rwononekaye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu gihugu cya Danimarike mu mwaka wa 2012 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki birenze urugero bishobora gutuma umuntu agira ubukana, indwara y'uruhu izwi ku izina rya eczema cyangwa dermatite y'intoki, kandi ko ari ibintu bisanzwe ku bakozi b'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi na byo ni kimwe mu bimenyetso by'uburwayi bw'agahinda gaterwa no guhugira mu byo umuntu akora.
Hari ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi by'umunsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ngombwa mu kugabanya icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane mu kanwa: nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero (kugwa, guhindagura), nyuma yo gusukura imvumba y'umwana (guhindura ipampa), mbere yo guha umwana ruswa, mbere yo kurya no mbere/nyuma yo gutegura ibyokurya cyangwa gukemura inyama zitagizwe, amafi cyangwa inyoni.
Ikindi gihe umuntu yakaraba intoki neza kugira ngo yirinde kwandura indwara, ni mbere na nyuma yo gufata umuntu waciwe cyangwa wakomeretse; nyuma yo kwishima, gukorora cyangwa gukubita mu mazuru; nyuma yo gukora ku bintu by'amatungo cyangwa gukorana n'amatungo; no nyuma yo gufata imyanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune ni ibintu byoroheje.
Mu mwaka wa 2015, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bihugu 54 bwerekanye ko ku kigero cy'abantu 38,7% mu ngo bafite ibikorwa byo gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Mu mwaka wa 2014, ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko Arabiya Sawudite ifite igipimo cyo hejuru cya 97%, Amerika iri hafi yo hagati na 77%, n'Ubushinwa ku kigero cyo hasi cya 23%. Hari uburyo bwo guhindura imyitwarire ubu buriho bwo kongera imihango yo gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu bihe bikomeye.
Porogaramu y'Iterambere ry'Ubuzima y'Icyiciro cya Mbere yashyizweho n'Ibiro by'Uburezi bya Filipine ni urugero rw'ibikorwa bikomeye byo guteza imbere ubuzima n'uburezi bw'abana.
Gukaraba intoki kabiri mu mwaka, gufatirwa mu myenda ya buri munsi n'isabune, no guhanagura amenyo buri munsi na florida, ni byo by'ingenzi muri gahunda y'igihugu.
