Mu gihe cyo gukaraba, amazi yo mu ntoki z'imbere agomba guhagarikwa ngo atange amazi yo gusubira mu ntoki.
Iyo barangije gukaraba intoki, barazikoma bakoresheje imyenda itagira inenge kandi bakambara imyenda y'ubuvuzi.
