Gukaraba intoki n'isabune isanzwe byatanze inshuro zirenga eshatu umubare w'indwara zandurira mu biribwa ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki n'isabune ya antibacterial. Ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki n'isukari ya antibacterial mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30, buri kimwe cyagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki n'ibikoresho bya antibacterial byaragabanutseho kwandura intoki 26% kurusha za antibacterial.
