Mu bihugu byateye imbere, gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni ikintu cy'ingenzi kandi cy'agaciro kenshi mu gutuma umuntu agira ubuzima bwiza, ndetse n'imirire myiza.
Ariko kandi, kubura amazi meza, isabune cyangwa ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu ngo, mu ishuri no mu kazi bituma kugera ku myifatire yo gukaraba intoki ku isi hose biba ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi.
