Gushyigikira no guteza imbere gukaraba intoki n'isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myanzuro y'ingamba, bigatuma abantu barushaho kumenya akamaro ko gukaraba intoki kandi bigatuma abantu bagira ihinduka mu myifatire yabo mu gihe kirekire.
