Gutegeka akaga ko mu kazi ka COVID-19
Ubuyobozi bw'Umurenge w'Akarere bw'Akarere ka COVID-19 ni uburyo bwo gushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bwo kugenzura umutekano n'ubuzima mu kazi mu kwirinda icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Kugenzura akaga gakwiriye mu kazi, bivana ku mwanya w'akazi n'akazi ukora, hashingiwe ku kigero cy'akaga ku isoko ry'ibyago, uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage, n'ibimenyetso by'akaga buri mukozi ashobora guhura na COVID-19.
Nkuko byemezwa na US Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA), akazi gashyize mu kaga ko kugira ibyo kabonetse cyane gafite umubano munini w'akazi n'abaturage n'abandi bakozi, aho ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura zigirwaho harimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, amahame yo guhumeka, no kwita ku isuku no guhanagura ibicurane mu kazi.
Imirimo ifite ibyago byo kwigaragaza ku rugero ruto ikubiyemo imirimo ikenera guhura kenshi cyangwa kugirana imishyikirano ya bugufi n'abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba bafite COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura kubera ubwandu bwo mu muryango cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Muri abo harimo abakozi bafite imishyikirano n'abaturage nk'uko biri mu mashuri, ahantu ho gukorera abantu benshi, ndetse n'aho gukorera ibintu byinshi.
Kugabanya akaga ku bantu, uretse kwirinda indwara z'ibanze harimo guhumeka hakoreshejwe ibipimo by'umwuka bikora neza, kugenzura ko umuntu atemba, no kugira ibikoresho byo kwirinda umuntu uhuye n'umuntu urwaye COVID-19.
OSHA ifata abakozi b'ubuvuzi n'abapfuye baba bafite ibyago byo kurwara COVID-19 ku bantu bazwiho cyangwa bakekwaho kugira COVID-19 nk'abafite ibyago byo kurwara COVID-19, bikazangana n'ibyago byo kurwara cyane iyo abakozi bakoze ingendo zo gukora aerosol kuri, cyangwa guteranya cyangwa gukemura ibipimo by'abantu baziho cyangwa bakekwaho kugira COVID-19.
Kugabanya ibyago by'abakozi bigira ingaruka ku kazi, harimo no kugenzura ingufu z'ubuhanga nk'ibyumba byo guhumeka bifite umuvuduko mubi n'ibikoresho byo kwirinda bikwiye gukora akazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka zitandukanye mu kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kuba batajya ku kazi kubera ko barwaye, ko bagomba kwita ku bandi cyangwa ko batinya ko bashobora kubangamira.
Uburyo bwo gucuruza bushobora guhinduka, haba mu bijyanye n'ibintu bifuza, ndetse n'uburyo bwo kubona ibi bintu (nk'uko kugura hanze y'igihe cy'ikirenga cyangwa binyuze mu serivisi z'itumiza cyangwa guhuza abantu).
Amaherezo, ingendo z'ibintu ziva mu duce tw'ubutaka twahuye n'ingaruka za COVID-19 zishobora guhungabana.
Gahunda yo guhangana n'ibipimo by'akaga kijyanye n'akazi n'akazi binyuranye harimo isoko ry'ibisanzwe, ibipimo by'akaga biva mu mimerere yo mu rugo no mu baturage, n'ibimenyetso by'akaga ku bakozi bose nko gusaza cyangwa indwara zidakira.
Ryerekana kandi uburyo bwo kugenzura ibyo bishobora gutuma umuntu ahura n'ibiza, n'uburyo bwo guhangana n'ibiza.
Gahunda yo kwitegura no gusubiza indwara zandura ishobora kuba igengwa n'itegeko ry'igihugu cyangwa ry'igihugu cy'ibanze.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo zirimo kugabanya ikwirakwira mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zikomeye, gukomeza gukora ubucuruzi, no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku zindi nzego mu mitego yabo y'ibikoresho.
Uburwayi bw'iki kigo bushobora kugira ingaruka ku buryo abantu bakira ikibazo.
Ihurerire y'ubuyobozi bw'ibyago ni ihame rikoreshwa cyane mu by'umutekano n'ubuzima mu kazi ryo gushyiraho ingamba zo kugenzura ibyago ku bw'uko bikora.
Iyo ibyago bya COVID-19 bidashobora gukurwaho, uburyo bwiza cyane bwo kugenzura ni ubuhanga bwo kugenzura, bukurikirwa n'ubuyobozi bw'ubugenzuzi, hanyuma bukurikirwa n'ibikoresho byo kwirinda.
Ubugenzuzi bw'ubugenzuzi bugira uruhare mu gutuma abakozi barindwa akaga ko mu kazi, kandi bushobora kuba ari bwo buryo bwiza cyane bwo kubushyira mu bikorwa.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubuyobozi ni ihinduka mu mikorere y'akazi cyangwa mu mikorere isaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi (PPE) byibonekeza ko ari bike ugereranyije n'ubugenzuzi bw'ubugenzuzi n'ubugenzuzi ariko bishobora gufasha kwirinda bimwe mu byerekana ko umuntu atagaragara.
Buri bwoko bwa PPE bugomba gutoranywa hakurikijwe akaga gaterwa n'abakozi, gushyirwaho neza hakurikijwe ubuhanga (cth respirator), kwambara neza buri gihe, guhora ugenzurwa, kwitabwaho no gusimburwa, iyo bibaye ngombwa, kandi gukurwaho neza, gukonjeshwa no kubika cyangwa guseswa mu buryo bukwiriye kugira ngo birinde guhumanya.
Dukurikije ubuyobozi bw'ubuyobozi bw'igihugu bw'ubuvuzi n'umutekano (OSHA), akazi gashyize mu kaga ko guhura n'abantu benshi cyane, nta n'ubwo gatuma abantu benshi bahura n'ibibazo by'akazi.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura zigenewe ahantu hose ho gukora harimo gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi ku buryo bunonosoye, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, amahame yo guhumeka arimo gukinga iyo barwaye no kwiyuha akuya, gutegura imyenda n'ibisenge by'umwanda, gutegura gukora imirimo ya telefoni cyangwa imirimo y'akazi iyo bibaye ngombwa, kudashishikariza abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho cyangwa ibikoresho by'abandi, no gukomeza gukora isuku no guhanagura ibicurane mu kazi.
Kwibonera no kwiherera vuba abantu bashobora kwandura ni ingamba z'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi bantu mu kazi.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga inama ko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bukomeye bagomba kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe batagaragaye umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso by'indwara nibura amasaha 24 badafite imiti yo kugabanya umuriro cyangwa imiti ihindura ibindi bimenyetso, kandi ko bagomba kugira gahunda ihoraho yo kurwara, bagatanga uburenganzira bwo kuguma mu rugo kugira ngo bita ku bagize umuryango barwaye, kandi ko abakozi bagomba kumenya kuri iyo gahunda.
